description:
Soak up the sun on Beach Day dressed as Rune Factory 4 favourites, Amber and Leon!

Get a helping hand as a rookie Ranger, with a set of items to get you started. 

The New Ranger Care Package Item Pack includes:
9 x Orange Juice
9 x Cooking Bread
9 x Tomato Seed
9 x Healing Potion
name: The Resplendent Butterfly and the Priest Swimsuit Set + New Ranger Care Package Item Pack
